channel.title: Help with 639 Client
channel.description:
Im using the eclipse 639 source and client ive ran the server and it has succesfully started on the port 43594 I have also changed the ip in the run file of the client to 127.0.0.1 but when I run the client it is stuck on ''Checking for updates 1%'' and after a few minutes the cmd file shows the error ''error_game_js5connect''.
Help would be appreciated, kind regards red
